  <brief_title>Helicobacter Pylori Eradication in Diabetic Subjects With Non-alcoholic Fatty Liver Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Helicobacter Pylori Eradication on Liver Fat Content in Diabetic Subjects With Non-alcoholic Fatty Liver Disease</official_title>
